Title: Step 8: Return to Marcus Eldridge
Text: Now that I’ve handed over the White Stag to the taxidermist, it’s time to return to Marcus Eldridge and update him on my progress.

pages: I’m pleased to inform you that your White Stag trophy is complete. The mount has been carefully prepared, and the stag’s head is now ready for display.

You’ll find it perfectly suited to hang on a wall, showcasing the rare beauty of this legendary creature.

It has been shipped to your address as per our arrangement. If you have any further requests, feel free to contact me.

Best regards,
Edwin Kellen
Feldpard Island Taxidermist

QuestMail.Subject: The rare White Stag, a symbol of the hunt’s success, proudly preserved for display.

CompleteText: I’ve returned to Marcus Eldridge to review my progress. The taxidermist will send me the mounted White Stag once it's ready. I’m now ready to move on to the next chapter.
